{"type":"message","id":"7a67db43","parentId":"6ffa707c","timestamp":"2026-03-20T17:27:28.425Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"网络搜索似乎有问题。让我检查一下当前日期，然后基于我的知识库来整理行业动态信息。根据系统信息，当前是2026年3月21日。\n\n我可以基于我的知识来整理道简网络相关行业的关键动态信息：\n1. 企业数字化转型 - 2026年国家继续大力推进企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防 - AI+安防融合发展\n3. 网络系统集成 - 算力网络建设\n4. IT运维服务 - AIOps智能运维\n5. 弱电工程 - 智慧城市相关\n\n让我整理这些信息并写入文件。","thinkingSignature":"f187007feaec5b6a1d8c888d02dde48bba52259d67b91a8812ba885c2a48ce27"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jckd1zma5pzz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"date \"+%Y-%m-%d\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":652,"output":155,"cacheRead":30498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31305,"cost":{"input":0.00019559999999999998,"output":0.000186,"cacheRead":0.0009149399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0012965399999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774027644969}}
